                           Directory Contents - /

  includes/
    These are scripts that are separated from the main script for easier readability.

  modules/
    All of the extra configuration files for programs are stored here.

  tools/
    Additional scripts to simplify tasks will be added here.

  logs/
    This is for the storing log files.

  tmp/
    This is a temporary folder for storing downloaded sources.

  config.ini
    This is the conf file for configuring some variables.

  COPYING
    Legal information is contained in this file.

  README
    Information on how to run the installer is written here.

  TODO
    This is a list of items that need to be finished.

  TOOLS
    This is a description of all the extra scripts in the tools folder

